        "ggVAXwM1zAm_text": "<p>To be honest, I barely have time to finish my coffee — let alone sit around for hours with a mask on my face.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>So when I first heard about the <strong>Nifora Bio-Collagen Mask</strong>, I rolled my eyes.<br>&nbsp;</p><p><i>Who really has time for a 4–6 hour skincare treatment?</i></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>But curiosity got me. Could one mask really do what 15-minute sheet masks never could?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I decided to try it — and <strong>my skin has never been the same.</strong></p>",
