        "ggf16hta2sg_text": "<p>“After juggling work and family, I barely had time for self-care. This mask made it easy. Just once a week and my skin feels hydrated and alive again.”</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>—&nbsp;JANELLE R., 41</strong></p>",
        "gg-Yzarg-Rl_text": "<p>“I’m post-menopause, and my skin became dry and dull. This mask brought back a glow I hadn’t seen in years. Even my daughter noticed!”</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>—&nbsp;DIANE L., 59</strong></p>",
        "ggGhBc9fcjD_text": "<p>“The mask helps me feel put together, even when I don’t wear makeup. It’s my go-to before events or long work days. I wish I found it sooner.”</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>—&nbsp;RACHEL M., 47</strong></p>",
        "ggCGFHtxy-X_text": "<p>I used to think I didn’t have time for a 4-hour mask.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>But now?</strong>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It’s the only step that makes the rest of my skincare routine actually work better.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Hope this helps you out!&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Xx Cerissa</p>",
